          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Since the difference in threshold for proton emission",
                " (10.3 MeV)  and  a-particle   emission   (6.2   MeV)",
                " a-particle contamination is large below energy about",
                " 18 MeV and it means that a-particles produced in the",
                " energy  of  about 13 mev appear in the same spectrum",
                " region as protons produced by  photons  with  energy",
                " about 17 MeV.  So the (g,a-0) reaction cross section",
                " was obtained  in  the  manner  similar  to  that for",
                " deducing of the (g,p-0) reaction cross  section:  by",
                " unfolding the   virtual  photon  spectrum  from  the",
                " topmost 2.17 MeV (the first excited state  in  Ar-38",
                " energy) of each photon spectrum."
              ]
            }
          ],
